name: Remix Icons for Figma
description:
Remix Icon is a set of open-source neutral-style system symbols elaborately crafted for designers and developers.
All of the icons are free for both personal and commercial use.

All the icos are Figma components and use a base fill style. In that way the search for specific icons is pretty easy through the Assets panel.

I (Jim Raptis) am not part of the team, just a big fan that wanted to share their amazing work. All the iconsâ€™ copyrights belong to the official Remix Design team!
